subject: College Athletics
Football
lead_paragraph: MiQuale Lewis ran for three touchdowns, and Nate Davis passed for one touchdown and ran for another Tuesday night to keep No. 15 Ball State among the nation’s four unbeaten teams with a 45-22 victory over Western Michigan.
